      (representation)

matrix
mat[n +1][n + 1];
mat[i][j] = 1 // represent i and j are connected

not usefull take O(N^2)

adj list
vector<int> adj[n + 1];

take only O(2E) space --> for undirected graph
take only (E) space --> for directed graph

---- about wt

mat[i][j] = wt;

in list we store pair adj[u].push_back({v,wt}];

